title: you will show me some respect- american horror story coven
author: ONCEUPON a HORRORSTORY
comment: Fiona Goode = The BEST AHS Villain ever.
I like Queenie but she should have took her own advice "You dont mess with the supreme"!

One of my favorite scenes from Coven. "You WILL SHOW ME RESPECT, YOUR SUPREME UNTIL THE MOMENT I AM REPLACED!" Love it! A lot of these teen witches were being real brats this whole season and we definitely needed a lot of Jessica Lange's hard core iron fist to set these girls right. AHS still would've been just as good as the earlier seasons if Lange had stayed with AHS all the way through. Seasons 5-7 would've been much better had she been involved.
